### api-gateway — smoke admin allowlist via X-Forwarded-For (set by gateway from peer)
### Run gateway + admin-service; replace @token after login.
@base = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_JWT

GET {{base}}/api/v1/admin/products?page=1&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Login (returns accessToken) — use body from your seed (e.g. admin@example.com)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email":"admin@example.com","password":"Admin123!"}
